result.name: Mask of Sichuen & Beijing

reviews.text: you could pay a visit here if you would like to be ripped off. firstly, there is no welcome or warm greeting from the staffs and secondly, the air condition inside the premises is very poor. they serve you peanuts followed by 2 or 3 varieties of sauces as a welcome dish, but later once you pay the bill, they will surprise you by charging $40 in the name of side dish and RIP you off and lastly the quality of food was from poor to medium. Definitely not recommended!
Awesome food for all! They have food for everyone, perfect meat, a veriaty of vegetarian dishes and also food for jains!
Awesome food! Great taste .. delicious 😃

I was a little upset at first when the staffs seemed to react reluctantly to my requests. Later, I realised that some of them were expatriates who didn't speak the local language. Service improved instantly when requests were made in English. Food quality was good for the price and we had a couple of pleasant surprises. It was an enjoyable evening out with friends.

A Beijing and Si Chuen restaurant with bar decoration outside, but there are masks of Peking Opera in the interior decoration.  The restaurant is quite large and suitable for large group of people dine in.  It's clean and tidy and the service of staff was good.  There are many choices of vegetarian food, it's good to taste traditional Beijing and Si Chuen food in vegetarian version.  Mostly of the food was tasty.  We cannot eat spicy food, spring onion and garlic, some of the food can be requested to be non-spicy and buddhist friendly.  The food was not oily and the taste was not too strong.  The price and portion of food was fair.  Chinese tea and drink was served individually.  Alternatively, we can order free water and can be refilled on request.
TST East station is for everyone especially in every year's X'mas to TST East for taking photos.

其實這個站原本是尖沙咀東( 應該是)， 尖東只是短寫。
其實之前這是九廣西鐵(西鐵線)九廣東鐵(東鐵線)的總站，也是荃灣線的中途站( 別誤會它真的經過尖東站，我剛才說的是指尖沙咀站。)。 但我不知道為什麼尖東站由 總站變成中途站。
超級大 的空間 …   哼！
舒適!
林明禎。。。

reviews.text: ツアーで来たお店です。連続6年ミシュランにのるお店らしく、コースメニューでしたがお料理は美味しかった。麻婆豆腐も辛くて美味しい！カクテル風のソフトドリンクもイイ！私が飲んだのはローズガーデン。お酒飲めなくても雰囲気味わえます。
